beer.beer_description:
Sticking to our award winning recipe for our 2015 Imperial Stout, The Mountie has been brewed to be a big beer with rich roasted flavours, without being boozy.  
The Mountie is a BIG, jet-black beer which delivers beautifully rich stout flavours including chocolate, raisins, and a roasty finish. In addition, we’ve added a heap of maple syrup bringing out a nutty, sweet character.
